{"type": "article", "id": 14901, "title": "皮质挂钩", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-15T07:10:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000313dCjBNJ2VyGZlqXHO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是一款皮质挂钩，中间有块热轧钢做支撑，非常简易。上半部分微微离开墙面形成一个空间，可以将衣物挂在上面，既不会使衣服变形，也不会因为沾上水而使挂钩生锈。此外，简单的造型能适应任何装修风格，不会显得突兀。有黑色和棕色两种，售价39欧，<a href=\"http://www.crowdyhouse.com/shop/twig-clothes-hanger/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142310hvFuyaYPERGl0DbH.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"730\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142310ULociPQxm4pknse9.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"722\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66851852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142311xBeUMpHDq3LJyZsY.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"705\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142312Gw10xUBFOA3JkRjD.jpg\" width=\"940\" height=\"679\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.72234043\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}